contracts/solidity/lib

# Rust / Stylus
contracts/stylus/target
# NOTE: Cargo.lock is intentionally NOT ignored. This is a deployable contract
# crate, so the lockfile must be committed for reproducible, MSRV-pinned builds
# (see contracts/stylus/vesting/Cargo.toml rust-version). Ignoring it caused CI
# to resolve transitive deps to latest on every run, drifting past the pinned
# 1.87 toolchain.

